{
  "stem": "6159.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were a group of people, and the leader always said that if I disappear and you don't see me, don't look for me because if somebody-- you know there were barbed wires all over the border-- and he said, if, if I disappear, that means that I saving my own life and I have to abandon you.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So you go on your own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So a few times he just disappeared, but he always came back when he saw that the, the air is clear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he cut a, a big hole in the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the meantime, they were patrolling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we heard shots, shots all over the place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when, you know, we carried a rucksack-- you know what is a rucksack?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I carried a rucksack, and that was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had about three loads of clothing on each of us, so whatever we could save, we saved.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course it wasn't easy to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was summer there, yes, June-- no no no, we arrived in June to Australia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was September, September, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was coolish already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we did is we, we took out a sheet of, made two, two knots on each side of the sheet, and we put my son in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we carried him because first we carried him and the rucksack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, my husband carried, then I carried him on, on, you know, holding him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after a while, I couldn't manage it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, I thought, I'm going to die with all this clothing in the rucksack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we, we made the sheet, and we put him in, and we gave him something to, to sleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how we got through the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
